<p>For products that do not display refund and replacement details on the product display page, will be govern by the standard Return, Refund and Replacement policies mentioned here and on Refund and Replacement Policy page on the Website.</p>
<p>If the User wants to instantly return or return within 7 (seven) days from delivery date of the Product, and <a href="https://ezcarestore.com/"><b>www.ezcarestore.com</b></a> does not offer reverse pickup of the items, the User may send the shipment himself/herself. The Users should send the scanned copy of the courier slip to <a href="mailto:care@ezcarestore.com"><b>care@ezcarestore.com</b></a> and Ez Care will refund the amount.</p>
<p>In order to confirm cancellation of order with respect to the Product, User need to indicate refund preference available on the Website.</p>


                       <p><b> Below are the modes of refund:</b></p>
<p>Back to Source - In this case, the money will be refunded back to the payment mode/account that was originally used to place the order with respect to the Product;</p>
<p>EZ Credit – In this case, the money will be refunded to user’s Ez Credit account which can be redeemed fully or partially while placing an order on our website or call center;</p>
